    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65374291720589312
    m_Localized: Setup
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65585418984890368
    m_Localized: Adjust the HoloLens so that you are able to see the four white markers
      in the corners of the fields of view.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65593364905074688
    m_Localized: Stream view to PC? (Debug/Study)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65609884557254656
    m_Localized: Other
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65610230469894144
    m_Localized: Language
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65645240300216320
    m_Localized: Last Pos
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 66066036042637312
    m_Localized: Keep the desired scene centered. The dot serves as orientation.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 67435629830676480
    m_Localized: The captured video is being processed...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 67507972779220992
    m_Localized: Tutorial
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 67516079332859904
    m_Localized: Tap "Start" to begin with the tutorial. Make sure to leave enough
      space in front of you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 67526327888191488
    m_Localized: "There are two ways to interact with your hands:\n\n1. <i>Near Interaction</i>\n   
      Tap elements directly with your index finger.\n\n2. <i>Far Interaction</i>\n    
      Point the hand ray towards a distant element and\n     pinch together thumb
      and index finger. Subsequently,\n     clearly spread your fingers again.\n\nA
      successful activation is indicated audiovisually.\nGive both a try!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 67531560487952384
    m_Localized: Near
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 67537737745637376
    m_Localized: Far
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 69706988007124992
    m_Localized: Handinteraction
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 69707268870303744
    m_Localized: Handmenu
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 69707637537042432
    m_Localized: 'The hand menu gives you quick access to important functions.


      Activate
      it by turning your palm toward yourself.

      If you are right-handed, the
      menu will appear on your left hand and vice versa.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 69711807816069120
    m_Localized: Test
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
