  - m_Id: 90642761954963456
    m_Localized: New Video
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 93517764752515072
    m_Localized: Is the desired action clearly recognizable?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 93532143241756672
    m_Localized: Checklist
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 93532335282159616
    m_Localized: '1. Action is clearly visible?

      2. Video includes start and
      end of action?

      3. Only the relevant hand is visible?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 98342393920823296
    m_Localized: to 3D
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 98353878319439872
    m_Localized: 'VLM

      (n. proc.)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 98360821272485888
    m_Localized: Are you finished authoring text and video?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 99014121726615552
    m_Localized: Previous
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 100125874900377600
    m_Localized: VLM-based
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 100504612100452352
    m_Localized: Are you content with the in-situ instruction?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 108808233086734336
    m_Localized: System generates 3D instruction
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 108809102041665536
    m_Localized: Let's go
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 115244573885931520
    m_Localized: 'Based on your captured videos, the system generates suitable 3D
      instructions automatically and organizes them spatially. You now have the options
      to verify and modify them if needed.


      As soon as all 3D isntructions
      have been generated, an acoustic signal is triggered and the button to continue
      will be unlocked.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 115716552011227136
    m_Localized: Are you finished authoring this step?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 115716746605961216
    m_Localized: Are you finished authoring ALL step?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 116071376993067008
    m_Localized: Create instructions
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 116071600553664512
    m_Localized: 'You can now begin with authoring instructions.

      From the
      menu in front of you, choose whether you would like to author:


      1. Textual
      instruction

      2. Video instruction

      3. 3D instruction


      Authored
      instructions are shown to you.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 117894296413523968
    m_Localized: No textual instruction yet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 118261088674607104
    m_Localized: brown
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 169725362853584896
    m_Localized: Delete?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 169962920091000832
    m_Localized: Edit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 169963253169070080
    m_Localized: Delete
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 169963888874561536
    m_Localized: Add
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 171515690443198464
    m_Localized: 'Edit the text:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 171799768589344768
    m_Localized: Regenerate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 171800359818436608
    m_Localized: Recapture
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 172624136253067264
    m_Localized: Delete or Manipulate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 172627224397467648
    m_Localized: Manipulate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 176235754621726720
    m_Localized: Do you want to redo this step?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 176240718102360064
    m_Localized: Redo
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 176248675837898752
    m_Localized: Are you ok with the video?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 176640528831705088
    m_Localized: '1. Create text, video, and 3D instructions

      2. Spatially
      arrange this panel as well'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 33455657302499328
    m_Localized: Begin Authoring
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 177737937348403200
    m_Localized: '1. Edit the text if needed

      2. Adapt the 3D object positions
      if needed

      3. Adapt this panels position if needed

      4. Demonstrate
      the step again if needed'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 178682666605027328
    m_Localized: Select starting step
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 178720571360747520
    m_Localized: Click me
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 178730795236794368
    m_Localized: Organize windows
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 178730949595570176
    m_Localized: "Windows can be reorganize if needed.\n\n1. <i>Anchored Windows</i>\n   
      Some windows are anchored in place. To organize\n    these, grab onto the upper
      edge using thumb and\n    index finger and move the window.\n\n2. <i>Following
      Window</i>\n    Some windows follow you around. You can organize\n    these
      within the spatial limits, too, by grabbing and\n    moving them.\n\nGrabbing
      on with 2 hands allows for resize.\nTry out both modes!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 178741317709537280
    m_Localized: Text and Video
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 178751528314982400
    m_Localized: Write something
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 178741484609282048
    m_Localized: "During the experiment, you will write text and record videos.\n\n1.
      <i>Text:</i> \n    Use the physical keyboard to write text.\n\n2. <i>Video</i>\n   
      To record a video, press the\n    record button. Say \u201CStop\u201D to end
      the recording.\n    The white markers serve as orientation points.\n\nTry both!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 178759036471463936
    m_Localized: Manipulate 3D Objects
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 178759472028962816
    m_Localized: "3D objects can be changed in terms of their position and size.\r\n\r\n1.
      <i>Position</i>\r\n    Grab the object with one hand (pinch) and move\r\n   
      it. Release by spreading your thumb and index finger.\r\n\r\n2. <i>Size</i>\r\n   
      Grab the object with both hands and move them\r\n    towards or away from each
      other.\r\n\r\nChange the position and size of the example object!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 178765449625194496
    m_Localized: Home
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 194382115692236800
    m_Localized: User Study?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
